org.lenskit.data.events

Class EventTypeResolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.lenskit.data.events.EventTypeResolver

  • public class EventTypeResolver
extends Object

    Look up event types. This class looks for META-INF/lenskit/event-builders.properties files in the classpath and looks up event type names in them.
